<% include ./include/head %>
<% include ./include/musicnotation %>
<body>
  <% include ./include/nav %>
  <main class="light-blue lighten-4">
    <div class="section white z-depth-2">
      <div class="container flow-text">
        <h2 class="header">Scales</h2>
        <p>Understanding how to build a major scale</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row container flow-text">

      <div class="col offset-s2">

        <div class="col s12">
          <div class="col s10">
            <h3>The Major Scale</h3>
            <p>Scales are made up of <b>semitones</b> and <b>tones</b></p>
            <ul class="bullet">
              <li>A semitone is a half step, e.g. from C to C# is a semitone</li>
              <li>A tone is a whole step and made up of two semitones, e.g. from C to D is a tone</li>
            </ul>
            <p>A <b>major scale</b> can be written as: </p>
            <p> <b>Tone</b>, <b>Tone</b>, <b>Semitone</b>, <b>Tone</b>, <b>Tone</b>, <b>Tone</b>, <b>Semitone</b></p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=10
                stave time = 4/4
                clef = treble
                notes :4 C-D-E-F-G-A-B/4 C/5
                text :4, C, D, E, F, G, A, B, C
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Here we see the C major scale made up of tones and semitones</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section white z-depth-2">
      <div class="container flow-text">
        <h2 class="header">Basic Major Scales</h2>
        <p>Understanding basic major scales including sharps and flats (Click each heading for a description)</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12">
      <ul class="tabs tabs-fixed-width z-depth-1">
        <li class="tab"><a class="active" href="#c">C Major</a></li>
        <li class="tab"><a href="#g">G Major</a></li>
        <li class="tab"><a href="#d">D Major</a></li>
        <li class="tab"><a href="#f">F Major</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="row container flow-text">

      <div class="col offset-s2">

        <div id="c" class="col s12">
          <div class="col s12">
            <h3>C Major</h3>
            <p>The C major scale has no sharps or flats</p>
            <p>The scale starts on C</p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=10
                stave time = 4/4
                clef = treble
                notes :4 C-D-E-F-G-A-B/4 C/5
                text :4, C, D, E, F, G, A, B, C
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="g" class="col s12">
          <div class="col s12">
            <h3>G Major</h3>
            <p>The G major scale has 1 sharp of F#</p>
            <p>The scale starts on G</p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=10
                stave time = 4/4
                key = G
                clef = treble
                notes :4 G-A-B/4 C-D-E-F-G/5
                text :4, G, A, B, C, D, E, F#, G
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="d" class="col s12">
          <div class="col s12">
            <h3>D Major</h3>
            <p>The D major scale has 2 sharps: F# and C#</p>
            <p> The scale starts on D</p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=10
                stave time = 4/4
                key = D
                clef = treble
                notes :4 D-E-F-G-A-B/4 C-D/5
                text :4, D, E, F#, G, A, B, C#, D
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="f" class="col s12">
          <div class="col s12">
            <h3>F Major</h3>
            <p>The F major scale has 1 flat: Bb</p>
            <p> The scale starts on F</p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=10
                stave time = 4/4
                key = F
                clef = treble
                notes :4 F-G-A-B/4 C-D-E-F/5
                text :4, F, G, A, Bb, C, D, E, F
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </main>
  <% include ./include/scripts %>
  <% include ./include/footer %>
